<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2023-11-04T16:31:42-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2023-11-04T16:31:42-04:00</published><updated> 2023-11-04T16:31:42-04:00</updated><title> 《堡垒之夜》舞蹈动作的版权之争又卷土重来</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Epic Games 徽标插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/K2AILwvzesQDkmioxcGlaJCj94c=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72829255/acastro_STK108__03.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图：Alex Castro / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;yENUbg&quot;>;本周，美国上诉法院法官组成的小组重新启动了针对 &lt;em>;Fortnite 的法律战&lt;/em>;通过逆转&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.gamesindustry.biz/lawsuit-over-fortnite-dance-dismissed-by-court&quot;>;驳回&lt;/a>;诉讼&lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.nbcnews.com/pop-culture/pop-culture-news/choreographer-sues-epic-fortnite-emote-kyle-hanagami-rcna23075&quot;>;去年&lt;/a>;由专业编舞者 Kyle Hanagami 针对 Epic Games 提交。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.billboard.com/business/legal/choreographer-epic-games-copyright-lawsuit-revived-new-ruling-1235461441/amp/&quot;>;&lt;em>;广告牌&lt;/em>;&lt; /a>;&lt;em>; &lt;/em>;指出&lt;a href=&quot;https://cdn.ca9.uscourts.gov/datastore/opinions/2023/11/01/22-55890.pdf&quot;>;提交的意见11 月 1 日&lt;/a>; (PDF)，美国第九巡回上诉法院法官理查德·佩兹 (Richard Paez) 写道，即使舞蹈的个别元素不能受版权保护，但编排却可以。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;66t1F2&quot; >;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nypost.com/2022/08/31/lawsuit-against-fortnite-developer-over-its-complicated-dance-dismissed-by-judge/&quot;>;下级法院表示&lt;/ a>; 舞蹈作品由无法单独保护的姿势组成。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;i4S7yY&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;史诗般的表情辩论：有关 Fortnite 正在进行的舞蹈诉讼的所有新闻&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2019/1/15/18184401/ epic-games-fortnite-dance-emote-legal-lawsuit-2-milly-carlton-floss&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Fortnite 的新赛季是一次穿越游戏历史的旅行&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https:/ /www.theverge.com/2023/11/3/23943701/fortnite-og-new-season-tilted-towers-baller&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id= “EFkA0D&quot;>;它发现&lt;em>;Fortnite&lt;/em>;中角色所使用的舞蹈编排的步骤和姿势“除了四个相同的姿势之外”并不“基本相似”，因为他们“没有共享任何创意”元素”...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23946260/epic-fortnite-choreography-emote-lawsuit-ruling-overturned&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23946260/epic-fortnite-choreography-emote-lawsuit-ruling-overturned" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23946260/epic-fortnite-choreography-emote-lawsuit-ruling-overturned</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-04T10:43:05-04:00</published><updated> 2023-11-04T10:43:05-04:00</updated><title>索尼的降噪 XM5 价格达到了迄今为​​止的最低价格</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一个人从棕褐色皮革钱包中取出银色索尼 WH-1000XM5 耳机。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/UUMXtF9_9MfTNJSxQlr4b9oz3Dg=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72828481/DSCF7932.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;WH-1000XM5s 仍然是您能买到的最好的耳机，即使索尼的命名约定仍然很糟糕。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;dTFUFU&quot;>;无论您是父母、经常旅行还是被迫出行的人，平静与安宁都很难获得聆听正在进行的建设，感觉像是永恒的——相信我，我会知道的。值得庆幸的是，&lt;strong>;索尼的 WH-1000XM5&lt;/strong>; 目前&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09XS7JWHH/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target= &quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/ckTQYqEzFSW&quot;>;百思买&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://goto.target。 com/c/482924/81938/2092?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fsony-wh-1000xm5-bluetooth-wireless-noise-canceling-headphones%2F-%2FA-86777236&amp;amp;sharedid =theverge.com&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;目标&lt;/a>;低至 328 美元（折扣 73 美元），与迄今为止的最优惠价格相符。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c -float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;AmJzoV&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;: “我们将顶级 ANC 耳机送到实验室测试其降噪能力”，“url”：“https://www.theverge.com/23852015/active-noise-cancellation-headphone-test-audio-lab” },{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 2023 年 PC 礼品指南&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23919557/holiday-gift-ideas-2023-pc-desktop-laptop-wfh-content -creator-tech-gadgets&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;您已经可以获得的最佳早期黑色星期五科技优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23899698/best-early-black -friday-tech-deals-amazon-target-best-buy-walmart-sale&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;UgJXFZ&quot;>;索尼旗舰耳机提供了一些自六年多前 1000X 系列问世以来，您可以在耳罩式耳机中获得最佳音质。此后，竞争变得越来越激烈 - 以最近发布的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23920591/bose-quietcomfort-ultra-headphones-review&quot;>;Bose QuietComfort Ultra&lt;/a>; 为例举个例子，但最新版本继续提供一流的 ANC 和清晰、自然的音频......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com /2023/11/4/23945130/sony-wh-1000xm5-amazon-fire-tv-soundbar-meross-smart-plug-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23945130/sony-wh-1000xm5-amazon-fire-tv-soundbar-meross-smart-plug-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23945130/sony-wh-1000xm5-amazon-fire-tv-soundbar-meross-smart-plug-deal-sale</id><author><name>布兰登·威德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-04T09:30:00-04:00</published><updated> 2023-11-04T09:30:00-04:00</updated><title> Echo Show 8 仍然是智能显示器中的佼佼者</title><content type="html">&lt;p>;增强的声音、小部件和 Thread 收音机是对亚马逊最好的带屏幕智能扬声器的良好（但不华丽）升级。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/23945192/amazon-echo-show-8-alexa-smart-display-review&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23945192/amazon-echo-show-8-alexa-smart-display-review" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23945192/amazon-echo-show-8-alexa-smart-display-review</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-04T09:30:00-04:00</published><updated> 2023-11-04T09:30:00-04:00</updated><title>如何设置 Echo Show 以向您展示最少的垃圾内容</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;矢量图显示亚马逊 Echo 智能扬声器和显示器的不同方面。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/tpdWk33pduMLms88izz95t7JhAM=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72828256/HT006_ALEXA_ECHO_SHOW_CVirginia.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;亚马逊的 Echo Show 是一款更好的智能显示器，没有亚马逊的所有东西。&lt;/em>; | The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;cYV50E&quot;>;亚马逊的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/e/23709233&quot;>;Echo Show 智能显示器&lt;/a>;确实很棒设备。价格介于 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09B2SRGXH?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;90 美元&lt;/a>; 至 &lt;a href= &quot;https://www.amazon.com/echo-show-10/dp/B07VHZ41L8?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot; Sponsored nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;250 美元&lt;/a>;（通常更便宜）亚马逊的永久销售），你会得到一个带有触摸屏的智能扬声器，可以播放音乐，向你展示照片，与朋友和家人进行视频通话，充当安全摄像头，兼作 &lt;a href=&quot;https:/ /www.aboutamazon.com/news/devices/connect-alexa-bluetooth&quot;>;蓝牙扬声器&lt;/a>;，并控制您的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23393163/best-smart-door -lock&quot;>;智能锁&lt;/a>;、灯和安全摄像头。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;7dS6QY&quot;>;但是，有一个很大的警告：亚马逊的硬件受到其服务的大力补贴，当您购买Echo Show，您实质上是将亚马逊服务的小广告牌带入您的家中。如果您按开箱即用的方式使用它，您将受到大量臃肿软件的轰炸，鼓励您使用亚马逊的服务，您很可能会想拔掉它......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot; https://www.theverge.com/23944889/set-up-echo-show-without-amazon-ads-how-to&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23944889/set-up-echo-show-without-amazon-ads-how-to" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23944889/set-up-echo-show-without-amazon-ads-how-to</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-04T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2023-11-04T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title>萨姆·班克曼·弗里德可能不是最后一个加密货币罪犯</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Sam Bankman-Fried 在翻滚的加密货币图形背景前的照片插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wcQHUB-4hEdJN7mJXtcgrTOB2K0=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72828126/236817_SBF_Trial_Stock_CVirginia_ SKETCHES_15.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Cath Virginia / The Verge 提供 |摄影：Bloomberg，Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;加密货币倡导者可能认为 FTX 的崩溃是一种反常现象，但他们可能很难说服公众相信这一点。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href =&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23945602/sam-bankman-fried-guilty-verdict-ftx-crypto-industry-impact&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23945602/sam-bankman-fried-guilty-verdict-ftx-crypto-industry-impact" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23945602/sam-bankman-fried-guilty-verdict-ftx-crypto-industry-impact</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-03T18:24:42-04:00</published><updated> 2023-11-03T18:24:42-04:00</updated><title>微软现在为许多 Surface PC 提供至少六年的固件更新</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;帐篷模式下的 Surface Laptop Studio 2，显示 Windows 11。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/fp2RRRtCByD9fDbRKcO-VwlUo_g=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72827056/236818_Surface_Laptop_Studio_2_AKrales _0061.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;K72qrI&quot;>;2021 年 1 月 1 日或之后发货的 Microsoft Surface PC 将获得至少六年的驱动程序和固件更新，根据&lt;a href=&quot;https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/surface/surface-driver-firmware-lifecycle-support&quot;>;微软支持文档&lt;/a>;报道&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.windowscentral.com/hardware/surface/microsoft-commits-to-6-years-of-firmware-updates-for-new-surface-pcs-going-forward&quot;>;作者：&lt;em>; Windows 中心&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;。此前，微软仅表示将支持自首次发布以来至少有四年更新的设备，如您在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://web.archive.org/web/20230923062247/https 中看到的那样://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/surface/surface-driver-firmware-lifecycle-support&quot;>;文档的存档版本&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;w6Qb68&quot;>;更改意味着，截至目前，Surface Pro 7 Plus、Surface Laptop 4、Surface Pro 8、Surface Laptop Studio、Surface Go 3、Surface Pro X Wi-Fi、Surface Laptop SE、Surface Laptop Go 2、Surface Laptop 5 、Surface Pro 9、Surface Studio 2 Plus、Surface Go 4、Surface Laptop Go 3 和 Surface Laptop Studio 2 都将获得至少六年的保修期...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:/ /www.theverge.com/2023/11/3/23945728/microsoft-surface-pc-six-years-firmware-updates-support&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/3/23945728/microsoft-surface-pc-six-years-firmware-updates-support" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/3/23945728/microsoft-surface-pc-six-years-firmware-updates-support</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-03T18:02:50-04:00</published><updated> 2023-11-03T18:02:50-04:00</updated><title>投诉后微软员工将继续免费使用 Xbox Game Pass Ultimate</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Xbox Game Pass 礼品卡&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/02nd16iJ-e5ZFlgcJEf_Ol7iDXc=/0x0:4232x2821/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/72826983/1234934021.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Beata Zawrzel/NurPhoto via Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;STp73H&quot;>;微软计划删除免费 Xbox一月份，Game Pass Ultimate 为其 238,000 名员工中的大多数提供了福利，但在员工投诉后，该公司现在正在改变这一决定。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/2/23944124/microsoft-xbox-game-pass-ultimate-free-employee-removed&quot;>;&lt;em>;The Verge &lt;/em>;报道昨天&lt;/a>;，微软员工对 2024 年取消 Xbox Game Pass Ultimate 福利表示反对，Xbox 首席执行官 Phil Spencer 亲自调查了这一情况。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;2izWzn&quot;>;Spencer 现已证实该决定将被撤销，微软员工将保留 Xbox Game Pass Ultimate 福利。以下是 Spencer 在公司内部 Viva 平台上向 Microsoft 员工发送的完整消息：&lt;/p>; &lt;blockquote>;&lt;p id=&quot;z2Q0Oe&quot;>;在与团队进行了更多研究后，我只想确认不会做出任何更改游戏通行证...&lt;/p>;&lt;/blockquote>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/3/23945294/microsoft-xbox-game-pass-ultimate-free -employee-perk-restored&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/3/23945294/microsoft-xbox-game-pass-ultimate-free-employee-perk-restored" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/3/23945294/microsoft-xbox-game-pass-ultimate-free-employee-perk-restored</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-03T17:30:00-04:00</published><updated> 2023-11-03T17:30:00-04:00</updated><title> TP-Link 的微型安全摄像头以极低的价格提供大量的服务</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/u1XLpR3_xa2Zht_3E8Pd3gF7W1g=/0x0:7008x4672/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72817472 /DSC9408.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;TP-Link Tapo 的新型室内/室外安全摄像头将很多功能封装在一个小包装中。 &lt;/em>; |图片：TP-Link&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;vqZtX0&quot;>;Tapo 是 TP-Link 的两个智能家居品牌之一，随着宣布推出$39.99 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tp-link.com%2Fus%2Fhome-networking%2Fcloud-camera% 2Ftapo-c120%2F&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2023%2F11%2F1%2F23941020%2Ftp-link-tapo-c120-indoor-outdoor-security-camera-价格-发布-日期&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Tapo C120&lt;/a>;。这款小型智能家居摄像头适合手掌大小，具有 IP66 防风雨等级，可在室内或室外使用。该产品将于 11 月 13 日发布。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;qZwWBG&quot;>;小型智能安全摄像头并不新鲜——Wyze 和 Blink 都有类似尺寸的产品，价格不到 100 美元——但 TP-Link 的新摄像头将许多功能塞进一个小封装中，价格不到 40 美元。它是一款有线摄像机，具有 2K 视频、带板载 microSD 卡的本地存储、免费的人工智能人员检测和易于使用的磁性安装座。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left&quot;>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：TP-Link&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Tapo C120 的价格.. .&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>;&lt;/figure>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/1/23941020/tp-link-tapo-c120 -indoor-outdoor-security-camera-price-release-date&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/1/23941020/tp-link-tapo-c120-indoor-outdoor-security-camera-price-release-date" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/1/23941020/tp-link-tapo-c120-indoor-outdoor-security-camera-price-release-date</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-03T14:01:11-04:00</published><updated> 2023-11-03T14:01:11-04:00</updated><title> Marvel 的 Echo 首次同时登陆 Disney Plus 和 Hulu</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;阿拉夸·考克斯 (Alaqua Cox) 饰演玛雅·洛佩兹 (Maya Lopez) 的图像。她穿着战斗装备，坐在机器上，看起来在战斗后精疲力竭。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/1TPx73KR7Kneeoq13sFy8x-YNvA=/0x0:5472x3648/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72826003/GRH_4T4A0362_R2.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Marvel Studios / Chuck Zlotnick&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;zsW3ge&quot;>;Alaqua Cox 的 Maya Lopez &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2021/12 /22/22849870/hawkeye-season-1-review-disney-plus&quot;>;当她于 2021 年出现在迪士尼+的&lt;em>;鹰眼&lt;/em>;中时，立即脱颖而出。在一群魅力十足的傻瓜演员中作为有着金子般的心的刺客，玛雅是一个可怕的致命陪衬，不断提醒观众和角色的利害关系。迪士尼非常迷恋考克斯对聋哑美洲原住民女英雄的描绘，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/5/17/23096167/marvel-echo-series-disney-plus-2023-第一个图片&quot;>;批准了衍生作品&lt;/a>;，周五我们第一次看到了它。我们还意外地宣布，该剧《Echo》将同时登陆 Disney Plus 和 Hulu。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;zKKzSV&quot;>;这条新闻&lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/2023/11/1/23875523/disney-comcast-hulu-stake-sale&quot;>;就在迪士尼承诺购买康卡斯特在 Hulu 的股份几天后&lt;/a>;，就像我们所有人一样开始想知道这对小型流媒体服务的未来意味着什么。 Hulu没有...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/3/23945203/marvel-echo-disney-plus-hulu-dual-发布日期&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/3/23945203/marvel-echo-disney-plus-hulu-dual-release-date" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/3/23945203/marvel-echo-disney-plus-hulu-dual-release-date</id><author><name>亚历克斯·克兰兹</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-03T13:44:10-04:00</published><updated> 2023-11-03T13:44:10-04:00</updated><title>谷歌取消与硅谷园区项目主要开发商的 150 亿美元交易</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一个混合用途空间，人们在绿地里闲逛，毗邻办公楼和圣何塞自来水公司的历史建筑。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Spuo_78_R_D-FvvtJ8aGexQ8eJ4=/80x0:944x576/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72825896/fVqGMEj8Yvvajhj6SqHF9HKKIra BP_VI.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;拟议的圣何塞开发项目的渲染。&lt;/em>; |图片来源：Google&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;LqGrgI&quot;>;Google 终止了与 Lendlease 的协议，Lendlease 是 Google 一直在硅谷四个主要园区项目上合作的主要开发商。在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.lendlease.com/siteassets/lendlease/shared/investor-centre/announcements/asx/2023/11/2635882.pdf&quot;>;周五早些时候发布的公告&lt;/a>;中， Lendlease 表示，两家公司在确定“鉴于当前市场状况，现有协议不再互惠互利”后，同意终止交易。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Y50hbh&quot;>;该交易覆盖圣何塞市中心西区、桑尼维尔市莫菲特公园以及山景城米德尔菲尔德公园和北湾岸。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.wsj.com/real-estate/commercial/google-ends-bay-area-development-agreement-with-australias-lendlease-7f6d59b6&quot;>;&lt;em>;《华尔街日报》&lt; /em>; 指出&lt;/a>; 开发项目的“办公、住宅、零售和其他空间”总面积可能超过 1500 万平方英尺。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot; >;&lt;aside id=&quot;AkUyc3&quot;>;&lt;q>;“鉴于当前的市场状况，现有协议不再是互惠互利的”&lt;/q>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;lijlIc&quot;>;Google 和.. .&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/3/23945098/google-lendlease-silicon-valley-campus-development-deal-end-housing&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/3/23945098/google-lendlease-silicon-valley-campus-development-deal-end-housing" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/3/23945098/google-lendlease-silicon-valley-campus-development-deal-end-housing</id><author><name>乔恩·波特</name></author></entry></feed>